Story*

Once opon a time in a forest,there lived a monkey who recided on a plum tree which was on the banks of a river.
In the same forest there lived a crocordile and his wife.One day,the crocordile came to the banks of the river 
and rested under the tree.The kind-hearted monkey offered him some fruits.The crocordile came back the next
day for more fruits as he loved them.As days passed by,the crocordile and the monkey bacame good friends...
